    man/openrc-run.8: fix mountinfo args.
    
    The "Ar" tag for the mountinfo command contained a typo (leading
    space) that resulted in the tag being output verbatim; that is,
    
      mountinfo ... .Ar mount1 mount2
    
    rather than e.g.
    
